title: Elastic and inelastic photon scattering on nuclei Fe-54, Ni-60, Mn-55, and Co-59 at the energies below the (gamma,n) reaction threshold.

x4freetext: Elastic and inelastic photon scattering on nuclei
Fe-54, Ni-60, Mn-55, and Co-59 at the energies

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Journal of Nuclear Physics, Vol.39, p.676 (1984)

x4freetext: Spectra of photons scattering on nuclei Fe-56, Ni-60,
Mn-55, Co-59 in the energy range of 5-14 MeV have been
obtained by means of the bremsstrahlung beam from the
NIIYAF betatron at the Moscow State University. The
cross sections are determined for the elastic photon
scattering, the scattering to the first excited states
of the target nuclei, the inelastic scattering to
groups of highly excited states; the total photon
scattering cross sections are also found.
